events.text:
The Psycho Sewer Saloon has shut down...
Permanently!!
Thanks to everyone for 187,425 years of PARTY!
There's a message scratched into the wood around the [color=#32ff00]Sewer[/color] lid.

events.question: Will you have a closer look?

events.text:
"[color=#fdff0b]MYTH[/color]+[color=#00ffc9]CAREEN[/color]-4-[color=#ff0000]ETERNITY[/color]... I MISS U EVERY SECOND!"
"Careen's favourite spell to walk through walls will keep me company in the coming days...
"LOL HERE IT IS: [color=#aeffac]dullboy33[/color]"
"Remember Careen's mischievous soul every time you [color=#aeffac]noclip[/color]!"
